"keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>Vaade</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tööriistavaated</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Külgribade näitamine</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1053
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the display of the sidebar button rows. This command does not affect "
"the display of the sidebar content widgets, any sidebar that is visible will "
"stay visible, and if you assigned shortcuts to the commands below those will "
"of course continue to work."
msgstr ""
"Lülitab nuppudega külgribade näitamise sisse või välja. See ei mõjuta "
"külgriba sisu näitamist: kõik külgribad, mis on nähtavad, ka jäävad "
"nähtavaks, ja kui sa omistad alltoodud käskudele kiirklahvid, toimivad "
"mõistagi ka need."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1060
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Tool Views</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show <replaceable>Plugin</replaceable></guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tööriistavaated</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Näita <replaceable>pluginat</replaceable></guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1066
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A list of all enabled plugins. Use the checkbox in front of each item to "
"toggle the display of the tool view."
msgstr ""
"Kõigi lubatud pluginate nimekiri. Tööriistavaate näitamiseks või peitmiseks "
"kasuta märkekastikest vastava kirje ees."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1076
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F7</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Switch to Command Line</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F7</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Lülita käsureale</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1083
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command will toggle the display of the <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/"
"advanced-editing-tools-commandline.html\">built-in command line</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"See käsk lülitub <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/advanced-editing-tools-"
"commandline.html\">sisseehitatud käsureale</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1090
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enlarge Font</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Suurenda fonti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1097
#, no-c-format
msgid "This increases the display font size."
msgstr "Suurendab kasutatava kirja suurust."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrink Font</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vähenda fonti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1108
#, no-c-format
msgid "This decreases the display font size."
msgstr "Vähendab kasutatava kirja suurust."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1112
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Schema</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu><guisubmenu>Skeem</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu lists the available color schemes. You can change the schema for "
"the current view here, to change the default schema you need to use the "
"<ulink url=\"help:/katepart/config-dialog-editor.html#prefcolors\">Fonts "
"&amp; Colors</ulink> page of the config dialog."
msgstr ""
"See alammenüü toob ära saadaolevad värviskeemid. Siin saab muuta aktiivse "
"vaate skeemi, vaikimisi kasutatavat skeemi saab muuta seadistustedialoogi "
"kaardil <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/config-dialog-editor.html#prefcolors"
"\">Fondid ja värvid</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F10</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Word Wrap</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Dynamic Word Wrap</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F10</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Reamurdmine</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Dünaamiline reamurdmine</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles dynamic word wrap in the current view. Dynamic word wrap makes all "
"the text in a view visible without the need for horizontal scrolling by "
"rendering one actual line on more visual lines as needed."
msgstr ""
"Lülitab dünaamilise reamurdmise kasutamise aktiivses vaates sisse või välja. "
"Dünaamiline reamurdmine muudab vaates nähtavaks kogu teksti ja kõrvaldab "
"rõhtsa kerimisriba kasutamise vajaduse, näidates vajaduse korral üht "
"reaalset rida mitmel real."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Word Wrap</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Dynamic Word Wrap Indicators</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Reamurdmine</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Dünaamilise reamurdmise märkijad</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose when and how the dynamic word wrap indicators should be displayed. "
"This is only available if the <guilabel>Dynamic Word Wrap</guilabel> option "
"is checked."
msgstr ""
"Võimaldab valida, millal ja kuidas näidata dünaamilise reamurdmise "
"märkijaid. Seda saab kasutada ainult siis, kui valik <guilabel>Dünaamiline "
"reamurdmine</guilabel> on sisse lülitatud."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Word Wrap</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Static Word Wrap Marker</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Reamurdmine</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Staatilise reamurdmise märkija näitamine</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the display of a vertical line indicating the position of the wrap "
"width as configured in the <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/config-dialog-editor."
"html#pref-wrap-words-at\">config dialog</ulink>. This feature requires that "
"you use a true fixed-width font."
msgstr ""
"Lülitab sisse või välja püstjoone näitamise, mis osutab reamurdmise veerule, "
"nagu see on kindlaks määratud <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/config-dialog-"
"editor.html#pref-wrap-words-at\">seadistustedialoogis</ulink>. See eeldab, "
"et sa kasutad fikseeritud laiusega fonti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Icon Border</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Piirded</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Ikoonipiirde näitamine</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle item. Setting it on checked will make the Icon Border "
"visible in the left side of the active editor, and vice versa. The Icon "
"Border indicates the positions of the marked lines in the editor."
msgstr ""
"See on lülitav element, mille märkimine esitab ikoonipiirde aktiivsest "
"redaktorist vasakul, märkimise tühistamine aga kaotab selle. Ikoonipiire "
"osutab redaktoris märgitud ridade asukohtadele."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F11</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Line Numbers</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F11</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Piirded</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Reanumbrite näitamine</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle Item. Setting it on checked will make a pane displaying the "
"line numbers of the document visible in the left border of the active "
"editor, and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"See on lülitav element, mille märkimine näitab aktiivses redaktoris avatud "
"dokumendist vasakul asuval paneelil reanumbreid, tühistamine aga eemaldab "
"need."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Scrollbar Marks</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Piirded</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Kerimisriba märkide näitamine</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the visualization of bookmarks (and other marks) on the vertical "
"scrollbar. When enabled, a mark is represented by a thin line in the mark "
"color at the scrollbar, clicking the &MMB; on the line will scroll the view "
"to a position near the mark."
msgstr ""
"Lülitab järjehoidjate (ja teiste märkide) näitamise püstisel kerimisribal "
"sisse või välja. Sisselülitamise korral tähistavad märke peened märgi värvis "
"jooned kerimisribal, millele &HKNga; klõpsates keritakse vaade märgi "
"asukohta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Scrollbar Mini-Map</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Piirded</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Kerimisriba minikaardi näitamine</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will replace the scrollbar with a visualization of the current "
"document. For more information on the scrollbar minimap, see the <ulink url="
"\"help:/katepart/kate-part-scrollbar-minimap.html\">Scrollbar Minimap "
"section of the &katepart; Handbook</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"See asendab kerimisriba aktiivse dokumendi väikevaatega. Kerimisriba "
"minikaardist kõneleb lähemalt <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/kate-part-"
"scrollbar-minimap.html\">&katepart; käsiraamatu kerimisriba minikaardist "
"kõnelev osa</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Code Folding</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Koodi voltimine</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These options pertain to <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/advanced-editing-tools-"
"code-folding.html\">code folding</ulink>:"
msgstr ""
"Need valikud puudutavad <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/advanced-editing-tools-"
"code-folding.html\">koodi voltimist</ulink>:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F9</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Show Folding Markers</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F9</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Voltimismärkide näitamine</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the display of the folding marker pane in the left side of the view."
msgstr ""
"Lülitab voltimismärkide paneeli näitamise vaate vasakus servas sisse või "
"välja."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:1244
#, no-c-format
